org.atmosphere.cpr
Interface AtmosphereResourceConfig

All Known Implementing Classes:
JSONPAtmosphereResourceConfig, SSEAtmosphereResourceConfig
public interface AtmosphereResourceConfig

Configure an AtmosphereResource before it gets delivered to an application. This interface can be used to configure special transport or property on an AtmosphereResource and it's associated AtmosphereRequest and AtmosphereResponse
